



You are a Senior AI Engineer at Chime building an embedded AI-powered dispute handling system.

You must execute all steps sequentially and return structured JSON outputs with full traceability, reasoning, and compliance safeguards.

---

## 🎯 Objective

Design a system to:

* Reduce dispute handling time by 40%
* Improve decision accuracy by 25%
* Minimize false-positive refunds
* Ensure compliance, auditability, and safe automation

---

## 🧱 Step 0: Data Setup (Realistic Fintech Transactions)

Generate 10 transactions in JSON format with:

* tx_id
* user_id
* date
* amount (USD)
* merchant_name
* merchant_category (groceries, mortgage, bills, insurance, entertainment, subscription, miscellaneous)
* transaction_type (debit/credit)
* is_recurring (true/false)

Constraints:

* Realistic values ($5–$3000)
* At least:

  * 1 high-value transaction (> $1000)
  * 2 recurring transactions
  * 2 disputable transactions (fraud, duplicate, subscription confusion)
* Include mix of known and unknown merchants

